flowchart TD
    subgraph ASSUME["`Four OLS assumptions  (LINE)`"]
        L["Linearity Residuals vs fitted: random scatter No curve = assumption met"]
        I["Independence Residuals uncorrelated No time-series pattern"]
        N["Normality of residuals QQ-plot: points on diagonal Required for inference CIs"]
        E["`Equal variance (homoscedasticity) Scale-location plot: flat band Fan shapes → heteroscedasticity`"]
    end
    subgraph FIX["Common fixes"]
        F1["`Curvature → log(y) or polynomial term`"]
        F2["`Fan shape → log(y) or WLS (weighted regression)`"]
        F3["`Outliers → robust regression or flag & re-check`"]
        F4["`Non-normality → OK for large n (CLT); bootstrap CIs`"]
    end
    L & I & N & E --> FIX
